content: As an AI language model, I don't have personal experiences or taste and I don't eat so I can't say if I have ever had a really unusual flavor of ice cream. However, there are numerous innovative and unique ice cream flavors that have hit the market in recent years. Some of the most unusual flavors include Avocado, Lobster and Fried Chicken, Garlic, Blue Cheese, Wasabi, and even Dil Pickle flavored ice cream. These may not appeal to everyone's palate but they are a testimony to the creativity and innovation within the ice cream industry.
